<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!--
  infiniti camera-port local manifest - promoted crDroid v3 split graph.

  Drop this file into .repo/local_manifests/ after repo init from the crDroid
  Android manifest, then run repo sync.

  This is the complete promoted composition: 36 projects, including 26
  infiniti-camera-port repositories and 10 external closure repositories, plus
  34 optional removals. The four shared common repositories use
  16.0-infiniti; every other infiniti-camera-port repository uses 16.0.

  The infiniti product has been validated. The other device variants are
  included for source closure, but their builds remain explicitly deferred.
-->
